parameters:
Explorer Armada: If you ever get tired of the Adventurer's
Guild, feel free to come and help me anytime.

Adventurer Armada: You've come well! Have you come flying
out of the Adventurer's Guild?
Clea: No, I'm still able to belong.

Adventurer Armada: That's a shame... Now, who could be the
magician?

Magician Relm: I'm the genius magician Relm! I'm a genuine
magician belonging to the Magic Academy!

Adventurer Armada: Ahaha, even though you're small, you're
quite something!

Magician Relm: Don't judge people based on their appearance
just because they're small!

Adventurer Armada: As an apology, I want you to investigate
something amazing that is in the back of the room.
Adventurer Armada: It's going to get busy from now on!

Explorer Armada: I've been exhausted from searching through
documents... Did you bring me something interesting to talk
about?

Clea: It may not be interesting, but I think it's a story
that will definitely not be boring.

Explorer Armada: U-Unbelievable... A dragon in Mount
Monimos?
Clea: Could you lend me your strength?
Clea: We need a force that can scatter the goblins.
Explorer Armada: They call me the heroine of Valier.

Explorer Armada: I'll join too! It's not like a woman would
just sit back and not fight in the crisis of Valier!
Thief Nora: Thank you very much! It's reassuring!

Explorer Armada: Since I'm indebted to everyone, if we
finish this, will you come help me again?

Explorer Armada: That's a good answer! Once you're ready,
we'll head to Mount Monimos.

events.name: 共闘者たち特殊並列実行

parameters:
Female Miner Armada: ...It's been about two days since the
cave-in accident, right?

Female Miner Armada: The traces of the ancient ruins we
finally found... I can't examine or see anything anymore,
even the candles have run out...

Female Miner Armada: I wanted to prove it... Ahahaha,
finding just traces is also fortunate, isn't it?

Female Miner Armada: So this is my grave... It's getting
cold... And I'm so sleepy... I guess... it's over...

??? I've come to help! You're not the kind of person who
would die here, right?!
??? 'Reach out your hand! I will definitely rescue you!'

Explorer Armada: Hmm... Ah, it's you guys... Sorry, I dozed
off even though I was the one who requested your help...

Explorer Armada: Ah, just a little dream... I was just
having a dream from a long time ago.

Explorer Armada: I'm sorry for causing you worry! It's
because I've been pulling all-nighters due to deciphering
the book.

Thief Nora: Not getting enough sleep is bad for your body,
you know!

Mage Relm: That's what researchers do! But more importantly,
the fact that I made a request right after pulling an all-
nighter...

Explorer Armada: As you can probably guess, I have
identified the location of the final accessory in the ruins.

Explorer Armada: The location is Mount Monimos, the mountain
where the dragon appeared!

Priestess Sophia: I feel like I'm sensing something like
destiny.

Explorer Armada: Let's meet up with Phoni at the entrance of
Mount Monimos. It's finally the last ruins, we need to brace
ourselves!
